    <title>css实现div水平垂直居中的多种方法</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/08/07/%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/08/07/居中/</id>
    <published>2018-08-06T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-26T10:37:47.201Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://47.106.244.20/hexo/images/%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD.PNG" alt="居中"><br><a id="more"></a><br>在one div中嵌套two div，使two div居中显示<br><figure class="highlight applescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;<span class="keyword">div</span> <span class="built_in">class</span>=<span class="string">"one"</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;<span class="keyword">div</span> <span class="built_in">class</span>=<span class="string">"two"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="keyword">div</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/<span class="keyword">div</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h5 id="1-父子元素-进行定位-子元素margin-auto-top-0-left-0-bottom-0-right-0"><a href="#1-父子元素-进行定位-子元素margin-auto-top-0-left-0-bottom-0-right-0" class="headerlink" title="1.父子元素 进行定位,子元素margin:auto;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;"></a>1.父子元素 进行定位,子元素margin:auto;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;</h5><p>css代码：<br><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.one</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span 